description:
I would never go again to this place anymore;
Yesterday they took forever(10 minutes )to bring me one glass of beer when I was eating although I was asking for it to the waitress and she  said "OH IT'S COMING " . What a disrespect for the customers ; I guess due to It was me only and  my wife ( party of two ) they didn't see a big bill so they didn't care about us .
And yet they have the guts to ask for a tip .( printed on the check ) don't bother to come to this place , it doesn't worth the money that you pay .
